<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>You've Been Invited to Join Only35!</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
  {{> header}}

  <div style="padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="color: #007bff;">You've Been Invited!</h1>

    <p>Hi there,</p>

    <p>A friend thinks you'd love Only35 and has invited you to join our platform!</p>

    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Your Referral Code:</strong> {{referralCode}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>Only35 helps photographers organize and manage their analog photography workflow. Join our community of passionate film photographers today!</p>

    <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Referral Reward</strong></p>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">When you sign up using this invitation, both you and your friend will receive a special reward as a thank you for being part of our community!</p>
    </div>

    <p style="margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{referralUrl}}" style="background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
        Accept Invitation
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      We look forward to having you on board!
    </p>

    <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 40px;">
      If you have any questions, please contact our support team.
    </p>
  </div>

  {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>
